  "text": "Free genistein was detected in extracts from young tobacco leaves expressing IFS and IFS/CHI fusion transgenes, but only after hydrolysis with b-glucosidase. A previous analysis of IFS transgenic tobacco plants could not detect free genistein in leaves [CITATION_1] . We could not detect genistein in mature transgenic tobacco leaves after hydrolysis (data not shown), suggesting that production and turnover of genistein aglycone and glycosides are developmentally regulated.",
